Communication between modules
A - pub/sub pattern
B - Using require.js ~config User Logged info may be exposed (Sid, Name, City) , Razor involved here...
C - Declare a MYNAMESPACE = {};
     each file extends your namespace through modules, then Namepsace.B will have access to Namspace.A
